7\f1\bullet  What is the difference between ViewState and SessionState? \par
\f0 answer=   View state can only be visible from a single page and not multiple pages. Session state value availability is across all pages available in a user session. It will retain values in the event of a postback operation occurring. In session state, user data remains in the server.\par
